<title>USA: Imperial Bancorp sets 10 pct stock div.</title>
<headline>Imperial Bancorp sets 10 pct stock div.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-01-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Imperial Bancorp, parent company of Imperial Bank, said Friday it had approved a 10 percent stock dividend, payable February 24, record February 17.</p>
<p>The company, reporting record earnings of $54.1 million for 1996, said it believes the solid foundation it has built this decade will continue its momentum.</p>
